# ğŸ“ **Directories (Folders)**

### â­ Common folders

* `/home` â†’ Usersâ€™ personal space
* `/var/log` â†’ Logs (computer diary)
* `/etc` â†’ Configuration files
* `/root` â†’ Superuser home
* `/opt` â†’ Installed software

